<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Neither the original material nor traces of this taxon were found in the herbaria consulted and among the documents accompanying the centuries distributed by Lojacono (
<bibRefCitation author="Aghababyan, M" journalOrPublisher="Bocconea" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="177 - 193" refId="B1" refString="Aghababyan, M, Greuter, W, Raimondo, FM, 2012. Michele Lojacono-Pojero's Centuriae in the herbaria and archives in Geneva. Bocconea 24: 177 - 193" title="Michele Lojacono-Pojero's Centuriae in the herbaria and archives in Geneva." volume="24" year="2012">Aghababyan et al. 2012</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.7320/FlMedit24.215" author="Domina, G" journalOrPublisher="Flora Mediterranea" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="215 - 232" refId="B13" refString="Domina, G, Greuter, W, Mazzola, P, Raimondo, FM, 2014. Names of Italian vascular plants published by Michele Lojacono Pojero. Flora Mediterranea 24: 215 - 232, DOI: https://doi.org/10.7320/FlMedit24.215" title="Names of Italian vascular plants published by Michele Lojacono Pojero." url="https://doi.org/10.7320/FlMedit24.215" volume="24" year="2014">Domina et al. 2014</bibRefCitation>
). We chose to designate as a neotype the single specimen found, which is at least collected by Lojacono.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
The neotype designated here matches the protologue and allows to consider this name as an heterotypic synonym of 
<taxonomicName family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="D." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="D. arrostoi" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="species" species="arrostoi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">D. arrostoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
C.Presl. Compared to the lectotype of 
<taxonomicName family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="D." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="D. contractus" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="species" species="contractus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">D. contractus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
designated by 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1756-1051.2009.00459.x" author="Bacchetta, G" journalOrPublisher="Nordic Journal of Botany" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="137 - 173" refId="B5" refString="Bacchetta, G, Brullo, S, Casti, M, Giusso del Galdo, GP, 2010. Taxonomic revision of the Dianthus sylvestris group (Caryophyllaceae) in Central-Southern Italy, Sicily and Sardinia. Nordic Journal of Botany 28 (2): 137 - 173, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1756-1051.2009.00459.x" title="Taxonomic revision of the Dianthus sylvestris group (Caryophyllaceae) in Central-Southern Italy, Sicily and Sardinia." url="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1756-1051.2009.00459.x" volume="28" year="2010">Bacchetta et al. (2010</bibRefCitation>
: 151: s.l., s.d., Jan, NAP-GUSS!), and to the lectotype of 
<taxonomicName family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="D." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="D. arrostoi" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="species" species="arrostoi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">D. arrostoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
designated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Camarda, I" journalOrPublisher="Informatore Botanico Italiano" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="415 - 421" refId="B10" refString="Camarda, I, Corrias, B, 1987. Tipificazione di Dianthus siculus C.Presl e di D. arrosti C.Presl in J. &amp; C.Presl. Informatore Botanico Italiano 19: 415 - 421" title="Tipificazione di Dianthus siculus C. Presl e di D. arrosti C. Presl in J. &amp; C. Presl." volume="19" year="1987">Camarda and Corrias (1987</bibRefCitation>
: 417), this variety differs only by the more elongated scapes.
</paragraph>
